{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act34side_level_act34side_04_beg","storyGroup":"act34side","storySort":8,"storyDependence":"act34side_level_act34side_03_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BP-4","storyName":"牺牲与代价","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"西昆妲意外得知数据员的隐情，失踪案有了新的方向。战场形势突变，尽管仍有顾虑，但在克莱门莎执政官的推动下，三位深海猎人加入航道计划，正式参与作战。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act34side/level_act34side_04_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act34side_04","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":6,"next":8,"characters":["卡西娅","阿维图斯","歌蕾蒂娅","克莱门莎","凯尔希","乔迪","艾丽妮","西昆妲","卢契拉","图利娅","“小帮手”"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_bg_51_g1_beaconsquare.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":5},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","id":6},{"type":"subtitle","text":"语音记录#21","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":7},{"type":"subtitle","text":"（未知语言，未知时间）","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":8},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act28side/m_avg_saferoom_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":9,"musicid":0},{"type":"subtitle","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":11},{"type":"subtitle","text":"......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":12},{"type":"subtitle","text":"瓦莱莉娅已经回来半个月了，但从塔罗斯发出的包裹恐怕是到不了了。那些珍贵的技术原型和生物样本，连带着我订购的那台民用级环境模拟单元，一同丧失了音讯。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":13},{"type":"subtitle","text":"没有播报，也没有事故报告，宇宙毫无征兆地对我们关上了门。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":14},{"type":"subtitle","text":"可怜的母亲，得在维生舱再熬些时日了。凭私心讲，是我坚持要在模拟环境里与她告别的。直到进入休眠的前一刻她还想着见见孙辈，我该怎么告诉她，她想象中的孙辈根本不存在？","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":15},{"type":"subtitle","text":"她一定是还活在那个枢纽铺满星海的辉煌年代，才会相信生命的延续不是徒增苦痛。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":16},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我为求稳妥才选了塔卫联合工业的产品。母亲太机敏，上一代的模拟技术她一定能识破。可我早该料到如今的星际运输有多大风险。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":17},{"type":"subtitle","text":"......","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":18},{"type":"subtitle","text":"瓦莱莉娅的假期用完了，她回去的时候仍在絮絮叨叨地谈着她那些宏大的使命，没有表现出一点遗憾。我不知道她是刚刚放下，还是早就不在乎了。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":19},{"type":"subtitle","text":"我早晚也会在那张同意书上签字，关停母亲的维生舱吧。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":20},{"type":"subtitle","id":21},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":22},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":23},{"type":"dialog","id":24},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#1$1","id":25},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":26},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$storyendjp_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act5d0/m_avg_storyendjp_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":27,"musicid":1},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":28},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":29},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":30},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":31},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"您怎么来了？","id":33,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"我来看看你，卡西娅。","id":35,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/70/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"你刚接受过胚胎分离手术，设施管理所应该允许你暂停工作好好休息。","id":36,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/70/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"您知道，胚胎分离手术对身体的损害几乎可以忽略不计，不至于需要休息那么久。","id":38,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"我一时分不清您是关心我，还是关心孵育室里的那个小家伙，阿维图斯老师。","id":39,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"我自然是关心你的，但一个新生的孩子，在如今的阿戈尔也同样值得关注。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/43/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"他降生之后，你会选择亲自抚养他吗，还是交给公共养育所？","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/43/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"我倾向于不去考虑这个问题。太遥远......太遥远了。","id":44,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"来见你之前，我去了趟医院。","id":46,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/70/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#6$1","focus":"r","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"医院？","id":48,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e7/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"昨天的那场战斗你肯定知道。你不会错过任何消息，对吧？","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/70/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"两支舰队，一千多名军团战士，最后仅仅只有二十六人幸存。","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/70/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"航道计划已经进行到最紧要的关头，弥利亚留姆却在此时遭遇了远航以来最惨重的牺牲。最近城市里也发生了许多异常......","id":52,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/70/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"阿维图斯老师，您想说什么？","id":54,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"海巡队已经去找过你了吧，卡西娅？","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/13/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"关于那个失踪的数据员......","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/13/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"阿维图斯老师。","id":59,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"......","id":61,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/9e/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"您知道吗，在您整理的所有文献里，我最喜欢的其实是那本《生活的死亡》，尽管它谈不上有什么学术价值。","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"那本书的出现只是个意外。","id":65,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/70/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"三百多年前，四位伟大的先史文明研究者在地幔遗迹群取得重大发现，无数珍贵的技术资料被带回了阿戈尔。","id":67,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"相比所有那些技术图纸和理论著作，一份日记般的语音文件确实是不值一提。","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"所以它静静地在科学院的资料库里躺着，是您出于好奇，将它们解译，制作成了通俗读物。","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"那不过是一个普通的前人类在漫长旅程中的喃喃自语。","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/70/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"但我很喜欢这个前人类的故事，老师。","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"我喜欢经由他的眼睛所见到的真实。","id":74,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"曾将无数星球统筹为一体的体制在崩塌，曾使诸多族类连成一心的信任在瓦解。物资的匮乏，技术的失利，哲学与艺术的沉默......","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"不论寄托了多少憧憬与想象，那些伟业最终都悄无声息地沦为死灰......就像信标塔里已经死去的那些浮游机械。","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/32/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"卡西娅，你在共情他的绝望？","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/13/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"我之前从没有在你身上看到过绝望的影子。你甚至选择让自己的孩子降生在一个随时可能面临毁灭的未来。","id":79,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/13/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"这不是绝望之人所能做出的选择。","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/13/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"我确实完全不感到绝望。","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b8/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"那个古板、颓唐的中年男人......我甚至很难以任何方式与他共情。","id":84,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"我只是很欣赏您借由他过去的见闻，巧妙地撕开了如今蒙在所有阿戈尔人眼前的这块华美的画布。","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"“我们必须接受曾引以为傲的事物和品质在此刻毫无作用，或许它们本来就存在瑕疵或谬误，是这场浩劫让它们暴露了出来。”","id":86,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"摆脱了生存的忧虑，人就会开始在意价值。我们期望自己的思想、作为，乃至存在本身都有价值。","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"阿戈尔的全套体制，都是为发掘人的价值而设计的。","id":88,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"然而价值是脆弱的。只需要换一个角度去解读，伟大的就会显得渺小，丑陋的就会显得美丽。","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"可惜，出于某种惰性，人们大多不愿脱离自己所熟悉的角度。","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":91},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"所以人们总是仰赖一成不变的价值而活，当这些价值崩塌的时候，他们也会随之崩溃。","id":92,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/70/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"是啊，就像您现在这样。","id":94,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"您的绝望是从什么时候开始滋长的？从弥利亚留姆离开本境开始，还是更早些，从您的密人离世时？","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1d/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#6$1","focus":"l","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"......卡西娅？","id":97,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/13/Avg_avg_npc_1386_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#11$1","focus":"r","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"不过还是感谢您今天来看望我。","id":99,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/12/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"您提醒了我，我确实还有需要完成的事，而时间已经不多了。","id":101,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/cf/Avg_avg_npc_1387_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":102},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":103},{"type":"charslot","id":104},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":105},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":106},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":107},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","duration":"1","id":108},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"克莱门莎，你竟然允许类似的悲观情绪在自己的城市蔓延？","id":110,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#2$1","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"《生活的死亡》，阿维图斯整理出版的先史日记。它在问世当年，成了最受公民们欢迎的读物。","id":112,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"窥伺一种陌生的生活，无聊而愚蠢的猎奇心态。","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"歌蕾蒂娅，这其中的只言片语，已经足以在陆地上的任何国家引发轩然大波。","id":116,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#6$1","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"一个微小的切面，靠着字里行间的疲惫与绝望，比任何数据都更生动地展现了一个辉煌的文明如何走上末路。","id":118,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"在如今的阿戈尔，它真的能算是一种“完全陌生”的生活吗？","id":119,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/56/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"阿戈尔是先史文明的继承者，但绝非其附庸。我们本不必对那些疲惫与绝望也产生认同。","id":121,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"阿戈尔之所以屹立不倒，在于它不可被摧毁的理性。","id":122,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#2$1","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"正是理性，让人们意识到阿戈尔乃至全人类的覆灭，是一种切实存在的可能性。","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"就连那些可憎的堕落者，他们的选择有时也出自长久的审视与慎重的思考。","id":125,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"你在军团服役的日子里，亲手处决过的深海教徒不在少数。","id":127,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#2$1","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"一如你不得不亲手处决那些失控的猎人。你我只是职责太重，没有资格依赖感性。","id":129,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#14$1","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"而您依据理性所做出的决断，就是让刚刚返回阿戈尔的深海猎人，贸然加入航道计划的作战之中？","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3d/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"凯尔希......","id":133,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#9$1","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"两位，请看我们身后的信标塔。曾经，它是前人所构想的星际征途的重要一环。","id":135,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"塔内孕育了数以亿计的浮游机械。最先突破电子云层的阿戈尔城市会将它们播撒在星海之间。","id":136,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"它们将自我增殖、自我修复，串联成长明不熄的路网。借助路网，我们的舰队将实现星际层面的自由跃迁。","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"海嗣危机爆发后，阿戈尔对星空的探索陷入停滞，需要由十几座城市共同维持的生物供能系统也被切断。","id":138,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"浮游机械不兼容一般的能源形式，失去了为它们专门打造的供能系统，所有浮游机械都“死”在了塔内。","id":139,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"但经过技术院同僚的协力改造，如今，这座塔依然能以另一种方式为我们点亮道路。","id":140,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"弥利亚留姆离开本境以来，一直在持续往海嗣巢穴内投放信标，海量的数据将汇集到这座塔的中控室......","id":141,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"通过对巢穴的精准定位，第Ⅳ级武器将摧毁目标海域中的主要巢穴，驱离盘踞其间的海嗣集群......","id":142,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"清出一片直通本境的澄澈水域——一条可供本境主力通行的航道。","id":143,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"海嗣或许会卷土重来，但至少在相当一段时间内，它们运来的养分会不断凋腐，它们重建巢穴的努力会徒劳无果。","id":144,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"执政官阁下，您是在向我们同步“航道计划”最核心的原理。","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#9$1","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"是的，医生。","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"昨天的那场战斗，深海猎人只来得及救下二十六人......海嗣明显已经有所准备。","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"从大洋腹地到大陆架，这座城市和海嗣缠斗了太久，海嗣对第Ⅲ级武器的适应加快了。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"第三十七号巢穴的位置过于特殊，它扼住了航道的咽喉......放弃它意味着功亏一篑。","id":151,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"这已经是航道开启前的最后一战，一切可用的力量此时都应被纳入计划，深海猎人自然也不例外。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#4$1","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"......哪怕她们才刚刚回到家乡。","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4a/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#5$1","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"阿戈尔是否能保障深海猎人安全归来？","id":156,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#2$1","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"新的战斗编队正在准备，他们将与海嗣正面交战，创造机会，让深海猎人得以潜入巢穴，投放信标。","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"但您知道这只是常规的战术布置。我确实......无法提供万无一失的保障。","id":159,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#14$1","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"既然如此......","id":161,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/3d/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"我知道你在担心什么......放心。","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"歌蕾蒂娅","text":"深海猎人的安全，由深海猎人自己保障，深海猎人的风险，也由深海猎人自己把控。","id":164,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/ef/Avg_avg_474_gladiia_1_1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#2$1","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"既然这是两位总战争设计师的共同决定，我不反对，但我保留我的意见。","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4f/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#3$1","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"歌蕾蒂娅......","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/57/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":169},{"type":"text","text":"感性的话语不合时宜地涌上了克莱门莎的喉咙。","id":170},{"type":"text","text":"她想要表达她的愧疚、她的悔恨、她的歉意。","id":171},{"type":"text","text":"她想要最后给歌蕾蒂娅一个拥抱，一如欢迎她回归时那样。","id":172},{"type":"text","text":"但她没能。","id":173},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#2$1","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"......歌蕾蒂娅。","id":175,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"布兰都斯顾问已经准备好你们的机体再生手术了，去做出发准备吧。","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_1382_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":177},{"type":"dialog","id":178},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":179},{"type":"charslot","id":180},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":181},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b2/Avg_bg_51_g4_aegirstreet_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":182},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":183},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$distressed_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_distressed_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":184,"musicid":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":185},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":186},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":187},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":188},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walkfast","id":189},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":190},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":191},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"艾丽妮阁下！","id":193,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/b/b0/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#2$1","focus":"r","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"乔迪。","id":195,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"您消失了整整一天......","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"跟着海巡队调查一些事情......我进入了一趟海洋，体验不是很好，别问了。","id":199,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"好。","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"你呢，你这段时间在做什么？","id":203,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我......","id":205,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"不适应是正常的。乔迪，打起精神来，这里可是你的家乡。","id":207,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"（苦笑）","id":209,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"看你的样子，你已经查过布雷奥甘的资料了？","id":211,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":212},{"type":"text","text":"年轻的阿戈尔人点了点头，又摇了摇头。","id":213},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我没法下断言，但我多半和那位伟大的船舶设计师没什么关系。","id":215,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"那又有什么所谓？","id":217,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"蒂亚戈叔叔希望我离开格兰法洛，离开伊比利亚，他没告诉我该去哪里......","id":219,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我是个阿戈尔人，阿戈尔应该会有我的位置。","id":221,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"可一个人总需要一点确切的联系，哪怕只是一个名字，一本笔记，才能真正追索他的来历。","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"阿维图斯先生说，即使被海嗣危机困扰了两百多年，阿戈尔仍然还有一百多座规模和弥利亚留姆差不多的城市。","id":223,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#10$1","focus":"l","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"如果我不是布雷奥甘的后裔，那我的祖父母，在他们成为岛民前，住在其中的哪一座呢？或者说，是那些已经消失的......","id":225,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"他们曾从事怎样的工作，过着怎样的生活......他们究竟是谁？","id":226,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/42/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"......","id":228,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"抱歉，我不该在您面前说这些。您明明也才刚来到阿戈尔，却已经能帮助海巡队调查案件，而我......","id":230,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"您是个坚定的人。","id":232,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/2c/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"我是个在这里做不了什么事情的伊比利亚人。","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"凯尔希医生负责与这座城市的领导者接洽，深海猎人回到了她们熟悉的战斗当中，而我的提灯和手炮暂时派不上什么用场。","id":235,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"阿戈尔允许一位黎博利参观他们的舰船与港口，但不会让她加入军团，同海嗣正面作战。我确实无法理解那种形态的战争。","id":236,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"在这海洋深处，我唯一能做的，只有调查城中正在发生的异常，尽可能为伊比利亚与阿戈尔的合作排除隐患。","id":238,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"您为什么跟我说这些？","id":240,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"乔迪，我的家乡毁于一场天灾，我对它已经没有太多印象。","id":242,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"我随身携带的经卷，便是我和家乡仅剩的联系，它救下了我的性命，成为我的指引，成为我的信仰。","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"可直到去过审判庭的地牢，登上“愚人号”，经历老师的牺牲......我才弄清楚信仰到底为何物，接受它的不堪，找到它的意义。","id":244,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"您是想说......","id":246,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/aa/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":247},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"乔迪，我没有你想象中那么坚定，我的困惑和迷失并不少。","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"只是更多时候，它会变成一个又一个亟待解决的具体问题。","id":249,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"逮捕作祟的深海教徒，夺回被海潮侵占的灯塔，找到失落在海上的舰船，以及，帮助我们的盟友调查一位意外失踪的数据员。","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"家乡也好，信仰也好，无非都是你刚刚所说的“联系”。继续找吧，你会找到它的，只是过程不会很快，甚至有些痛苦。","id":251,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我，能吗？","id":253,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_avg_npc_1380_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","focus":"r","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"不能吗？","id":255,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"你帮助伊比利亚点亮了最后的灯塔，也救起过三位深海猎人。劳伦缇娜小姐不是说过嘛，这足以得到执政官本人的表彰。","id":256,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"无论是作为阿戈尔人，还是审判庭的书记，你都能做到很多事情。","id":257,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":258},{"type":"dialog","id":259},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":260},{"type":"charslot","id":261},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":262},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_bg_51_g1_beaconsquare.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":263},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":264},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loading_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_sys_loading_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":265,"musicid":3},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":266},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","id":267},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"......","id":269,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":270},{"type":"charslot","id":271},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":272},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#5$1","duration":"1","id":273},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":274},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#5$1","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"长官！","id":276,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a5/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"您已经回到了城里......看您的表情，调查并不顺利，对吗？","id":278,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"卢契拉小姐？","id":280,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"抱歉，我正准备向克莱门莎执政官汇报案情的进展，具体的情况不方便透露。","id":281,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#5$1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"其实、其实我有事找您。","id":283,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a5/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"上次您找我和卡西娅了解情况的时候，我就应该想起来的。只是很小很小的一件事情，或许对整个案件压根没什么帮助。","id":285,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"但我真的很在意！","id":286,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"......请说。","id":288,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":289},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":290},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":291},{"type":"charslot","id":292},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":293},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","keep":"true","initamount":"0","amount":"0.7","block":"true","id":294},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/65/Avg_bg_51_g5_aegirstreet_2.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":295},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":296},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/a001/m_dia_path_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":297,"musicid":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":298},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":299},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"......","id":301,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"图利娅小姐，你是留到最后的研究员。","id":303,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#8$1","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"抱歉抱歉，能不能再给我一点时间？","id":305,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/15/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#1$1","id":306},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"古球藻、团窗藻、石花膜、紫苔、千灯英......剩下的不多了，我很快就能清点完！","id":307,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","id":308},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"图利娅小姐，不用着急，我只是来例行检查而已。","id":309,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#1$1","id":310},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"您认识我？","id":311,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"嗯，之前发展规划所进行转岗评估，我们是同一批，你可能没有注意到我。","id":313,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"你是准备，带走这些海藻？","id":314,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#4$1","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"这、这应该不违反什么程序吧？","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/13/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"别紧张。这栋建筑的交接工作已经完成了......留下来的这些海藻植株和培育设备，你不带走，最后也只能批量清理。","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#11$1","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"谢谢。","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"可是这么多海藻，你也没办法把它们全部带走吧。","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"而且为了靠近陆地作业，弥利亚留姆接下来会进行针对性改造，城里也不再有培育海藻的空间和资源。","id":323,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#11$1","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"嗯嗯，我知道。","id":325,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"能带走多少就带走多少......我会想办法，不给大家添麻烦。","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#10$1","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"可之前火山边的那座基地都被......","id":328,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/0a/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#3$1","id":329},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"那是阿戈尔最大的濒危植物繁育基地，我看着它被海嗣吞没。","id":330,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/da/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#1$1","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"这些原始藻类是整片海洋里最简单，却也最顽强的生命。","id":332,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"不论明亮的浅海，还是无光的深渊，不论平滑的海床，还是断崖的夹缝，它们都在努力地舒展身躯。","id":333,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"它们与海洋同岁，是这颗星球的活化石。","id":334,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"我不是军团的人，没法直接去斩杀海嗣，这些残留的海藻，也没办法帮我们解决海嗣问题。","id":335,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#9$1","id":336},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"但我不能看着它们就这么枯萎在这里。","id":337,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/30/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","id":338},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......图利娅小姐，你很热爱这份工作。","id":339,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#1$1","id":340},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"唔，您不是吗？","id":341,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/10/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#4$1","id":342},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......","id":343,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-4$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#8$1","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"啊，我的小帮手把装载模块送过来了，我就不和您聊了。","id":345,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/15/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","id":346},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"要帮忙吗？","id":347,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1385_1#11$1","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"图利娅","text":"不用了，谢谢。","id":349,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_avg_npc_1385_1-11$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":350},{"type":"dialog","id":351},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":352},{"type":"charslot","id":353},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":354},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/62/Avg_bg_51_g1_beaconsquare.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":355},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":356},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loading_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_sys_loading_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":357,"musicid":5},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","id":358},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"什么时候的事情？","id":359,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","id":360},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"生态艺术创作所搬迁的前一天。","id":361,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我不知道她到底出了什么事，也不知道在她的眼里，到底是不是弥利亚留姆放弃了那座火山能源站，放弃了那个繁育基地......","id":362,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"但我更想象不到她会因此去做什么不好的事情......因为她自己从来没有放弃过什么。","id":363,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":364},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1","id":365},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"图利娅的住所确实存放着一批水培箱，但已经空置很久......","id":367,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/60/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":368},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":369},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":370},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":371},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"卢契拉小姐，你刚刚说的，或许并非无足轻重的小事。","id":372,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"只是，容我冒昧地问一句，你为何对图利娅的事情格外关注？","id":373,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"按照我之前听到的，你们连朋友都算不上。","id":374,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","id":375},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"她......","id":376,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"她身上有我没有的东西。","id":377,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/fb/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","id":378},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"好了，该说的都说完了。长官，我得赶紧回去工作。","id":379,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"最近事情越来越多，城市单元骨架的检修量翻了好几倍，我的墨水都不够用了。","id":380,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d5/Avg_avg_4079_haini_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":381},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":382},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":383},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":384},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"小帮手。","id":386,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f0/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1401_1#1$1","id":387},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“小帮手”","text":"西昆妲指挥官。","id":388,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e4/Avg_avg_npc_1401_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","id":389},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"立刻向设施管理所调取弥利亚留姆的城市资料，检索具有封闭水培条件的场所。","id":390,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"另外，联系艾丽妮——","id":391,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"图利娅或许还在城内留下了其他线索，请她尽快与我会合。","id":392,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_avg_4137_udflow_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":393},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":394},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":395},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":396},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":397},{"type":"image","id":398},{"type":"charslot","id":399}],"characters":["卡西娅","阿维图斯","歌蕾蒂娅","克莱门莎","凯尔希","乔迪","艾丽妮","西昆妲","卢契拉","图利娅","“小帮手”"]}